n automotive engineering from the sae he also received awards in  for outstanding achievements in mechanical engineering from the american society of mechanical engineers mr coates has extensive experience in international corporate business and has developed many long time associates and contacts in the business and scientific communities around the world     education   city and guilds of london institute the college of technology equivalence be bs me ee mechanical engineering electrical engineering physical science motor engineering certificate – all with honors the american society of mechanical engineers awarded for outstanding achievement in mechanical engineering october   awarded associate member sae the engineering society for advancing mobility land sea air and space international licensed inspector the presidential business commission chairman and executive committee appointed george jcoates to the presidential business commission of the united states of america activities and societies of the job engineering instructor anco the industrial training authority amalgamated engineering union london se el uk b l m c r r mercedes benz scr motor engineers coates engineering ltd europe design engineering coates international ltd usa rd he is an accomplished musician he plays piano and many other musical instruments as well as composes music     family george j coates and bernadette coates learn more george j coates and bernadette coates – honeymoon  learn more coates family history “of the coast”   the name coates is of ancient origin and was written in the earliest records as de cote meaning from the coast it was a norman name and the letter “a” was added to help in the correct pronunciation in english the “a” occurs in the spelling as early as  when in the fourth year of edward iii william de coates was lord of coles deville in leicestershire england and again in  john de coates with an “a” held lands in lincoln although the name was generally written cotes until the seventeenth century there are landed proprietors bearing the name coates in england wales and ireland the first coates family arrived in ireland in the early s shortly after arriving in ireland the family bought land in kildare around donadea kilcock and ovidstown from the aylmer family where they built their family estate at knockanally they also had a house in brighton england matthew coates esq built the original knockanally house which was to stand for almost  years this was built in the late ’s and he was the first of four generations of the coates family to own knockanally he was known to locals as “miner” coates a reference to mines he owned in africa his son william coates esq built the present knockanally house in  he was the local magistrate in the area of enfield the estate remained the ancestral home of the coates family until  when it was sold to the irish land commission and redestributed to irish families the house still remains today and is the club house of the knockanally golf course nowadays the family is spread out over five counties dublin wicklow westmeath meath and kildare   the coates family moved to dublin in the  and opened a piano factory joseph jennings coates from eccleshill in yorkshire england was a composer pianist and piano tuner his wife jessie coates was a professor of music from exeter in devonshire england since then the family have always had a very musical background his son ernest and his wife emily were also pianists and music teachers most of their children including harold richard and frederick became musicians able to play repair and tune many instruments in time both richards and fredericks children followed in their footsteps forming several bands that played all over england and ireland       the musical history second nature  from top rachael olivia and virginia coates gemini  gwen coates walsh  norman coates catherine coates singerfront cover of one of her albums john coates singersongwriter poster of rose coat